{"segment_id": "shijing__song-chengong-003__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "song-chengong-003", "source_id": "song-chengong-003__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·頌·臣工之什·003.1", "text_original": "振鷺于飛，于彼西雝。我客戾止，亦有斯容。", "text_normalized": "振鷺于飛，于彼西雝。我客戾止，亦有斯容。", "notes": "振鷺 Chinese stanza 1."}
